sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant CLI as CLI / API
    participant Manager as Workflow Manager
    participant Collector as Source Collector
    participant Extractor as Listing Extractor
    participant Comp as Comp Researcher
    participant Margin as Margin Analyst
    participant Ranker as Reviewer / Ranker

    User->>CLI: Submit query\n"vintage lamp"
    CLI->>Manager: Start opportunity search
    Manager->>Collector: Gather second-hand listings
    Collector-->>Manager: Candidate listings
    Manager->>Extractor: Normalize each listing
    Extractor-->>Manager: Structured item records
    Manager->>Comp: Find resale comparables
    Comp-->>Manager: Comparable sold/listed prices
    Manager->>Margin: Estimate conservative margin
    Margin-->>Manager: Profit, margin %, confidence
    Manager->>Ranker: Reject weak items and sort the rest
    Ranker-->>Manager: Ranked opportunities
    Manager-->>CLI: Final response
    CLI-->>User: Table or JSON output

    Note over User,CLI: Demo entrypoints: `uv run second-hand-agents ...` or `POST /opportunities/search`
    Note over Manager,Ranker: In demo mode, the workflow is deterministic and stable for presentation
